main.name: SCONRES4
main.longTitle: CONCURRENT RESOLUTION Providing for a correction in the enrollment of H.J. Res.31.
main.enactingFormula: Resolved by the Senate (the House of Representatives concurring),

section.content: That, in the enrollment of the joint resolution H.J. Res. 31, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall amend the long title so as to read: “Making consolidated appropriations for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2019, and for other purposes.”.

signature.role: Clerk of the House of Representatives
